        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1278517253" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13585407905777172261">When I started Vol. 1, I said I wanted books that took up years of my life. The first one didn’t quite— it took less than three months— but now the second one has filled that bill. And I couldn’t ask for a better one to take up that time.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


