<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/13531850-the-man-who-saved-the-union"><img alt="The Man Who Saved the Union: Ulysses Grant in War and Peace" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1333578255l/13531850._SX98_.jpg" />
